  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_25",
    "english": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire.",
    "japanese": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire.",
    "korean": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire.",
    "spanish": "Demon. Hell Knight. Aide of Edwin Black, the leader of a multinational company Nomad. She's always by his side as a secretary and a guard. She is cold to everyone apart from Edwin Black and is not on good terms with Oboro, Nomad's executive.\n\nShe's a descendant of a royal class demon. She looks no different from a human being, but boasts strength that far outweighs a human's. She swings a longsword that ignites her enemies on fire."
  },
